data.description: Introducing a stunning four-bedroom, two-bathroom home nestled on a spacious one fourth of an -acre lot, conveniently located across from Boyd High School. This modern gem was crafted with meticulous attention to detail, boasting a timeless architectural design and completed in 2013. One of the highlights of this property is the charming two-car garage, providing ample space for vehicles and storage. As you step into this inviting home, you are greeted by a warm and welcoming ambiance, thanks to its well-thought-out floor plan. The living spaces are thoughtfully designed for both entertaining and relaxation, with a seamless flow that creates an airy and spacious feel throughout. The sleek and stylish kitchen steals the spotlight, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and elegant cabinetry, perfect for preparing culinary delights and hosting memorable gatherings.
